headline: Geotab and Thermo King Collaborate to Preserve Perishables
summary: Geotab Inc. and its affiliates ("Geotab"), a global leader in connected vehicle and asset solutions, today announced a collaboration with Thermo King, a leader in sustainable transport temperature control solutions and a strategic brand of global climate innovator Trane Technologies (NYSE: TT).
